July 28, 2017 8:43 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Rafferty Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Rafferty Asset Management, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies. It also caters to pooled investment vehicles. The firm manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets. The firm was founded in 1997 and is based in New York City. Rafferty Asset Management, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Rafferty Capital Markets, LLC.


1301 Avenue of the Americas35th FloorNew York, NY 10019United StatesFounded in 1997



Phone: 646-572-3390

Fax: 646-572-3498








