Rafferty Asset Management, LLC is a privately owned investment firm which provides institutional securities brokerage services and operates as a subsidiary of Rafferty Capital Markets, LLC. Rafferty Capital Markets, LLC provides institutional securities brokerage services. Rafferty Capital Markets, LLC was… MoreRafferty Asset Management, LLC is a privately owned investment firm which provides institutional securities brokerage services and operates as a subsidiary of Rafferty Capital Markets, LLC. Rafferty Capital Markets, LLC provides institutional securities brokerage services. Rafferty Capital Markets, LLC was founded in 1987 and operates as a subsidiary of Rafferty Holdings, LLC






